2.3 DUIM-Geometry Module

region-empty?

Generic function

Summary

Returns #t if the region is empty.

Signature

region-empty? region => boolean

Arguments

region
An instance of type <region>.

Values

boolean
An instance of type <boolean>.

Library

duim-geometry

Module

duim-geometry

Description

Returns #t if the region is empty, otherwise returns #f.
